<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khuaruahhar vel a va thlum dah, Kei santlai lo a khamh, Ka rak tlau
 nain a ka hmuh, Ka mit a deiter than.

[V2]
 Cu ral nih ka phannak a hloh, Tihnak vialte an lo, Zumhnak ka ngeih
 hnu in ka hngalh, Cu vel a sunlawi zia.

[V3]
 Tihphan awk le harnak phun kip, Ton bu in ka ra cang, Cu vel nih cun
 ka hna ngamter, Inn ah a ka hruai lai.

[V4]
 Zungzal hmun nuam kan um hnu cun, Ni bangin kan ceu lai, Pathian kan
 thangthat zungzal lai, Thabat a um lai lo.</lyrics>
<title>KHUARUAHHAR VEL CH75</title>
<hymn_number>75</hymn_number>
</song>